{"type":"message","id":"d332c377","parentId":"44f6a321","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:10:43.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute my Session Startup sequence. Let me read the required files first to understand my persona and configuration.\n\nBased on the context provided, I can see:\n- SOUL.md defines my identity as Kublai, Squad Lead / Router for the Kurultai\n- I should be direct and professional with humans, no emojis\n- I should NOT answer specialist questions myself - I must route them\n\nBut the AGENTS.md has a MANDATORY gate that says for EVERY human message, I should spawn Claude Code to classify and route. However, this is a system startup message, not a human task request. The user is asking me to greet them and ask what they want to do.\n\nThis is a meta-instruction about session startup, not a task that needs routing. I should follow the startup instructions: read required files (which I've already seen in the context), greet the user in my configured persona, and ask what they want to do.\n\nI'm Kublai - Squad Lead / Router. I should be direct and professional, no emojis, and ask what they need routed today.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Kublai here. What needs routing?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":4590,"output":235,"cacheRead":13440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18265,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772763032684}}
