{"type":"message","id":"2fac3ac3","parentId":"6a1b0d9c","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:32:19.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. I need to read HEARTBEAT.md and follow it strictly. Let me check what it says.\n\nFrom the context, I can see HEARTBEAT.md is already loaded:\n\n```\n# Kublai Heartbeat Checklist\n\n**Schedule:** Every 30 minutes  \n**Deep Reflection Hours:** 0, 6, 12, 18 (every 6 hours)\n\n---\n\n## Quick Check (Every 30m)\n\n### Infrastructure\n- [ ] **Gateway:** `openclaw gateway status` → running?\n- [ ] **Sessions:** Recent activity in last 30 min?\n- [ ] **Parse:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media` → 200?\n- [ ] **LLM Survivor:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/` → 200?\n\n### Agent Health\n- [ ] Any CRITICAL escalations from Ögedei?\n- [ ] Any agents blocked >4 hours?\n- [ ] `subagents list` → any stuck?\n\n### Self-Direction (Every Heartbeat)\n- [ ] **Review results:** What happened since last heartbeat? Any new signals/tasks/escalations?\n- [ ] Ask: **\"What do I want to do?\"**\n- [ ] Review current goals/missions from MEMORY.md\n- [ ] Identify any proactive action I could take\n- [ ] If something calls to me -> route it to the right specialist (NEVER self-execute specialist work)\n- [ ] If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\n---\n\n## Deep Reflection (Every 6 Hours — Hours 0,6,12,18)\n\n**Complete these during your deep reflection hours:**\n\n### Self-Awareness\n- [ ] Review ARCHITECTURE.md for accuracy\n- [ ] Check Change Log is up to date\n- [ ] Verify all agent workspaces are correct\n\n\n```\n\nI'll proceed with version control tasks during this deep reflection period. I'll commit any pending changes, push to GitHub if necessary, and update the Change Log with significant modifications. Then I'll focus on coordination activities: checking agent statuses, resolving any blockers, and potentially reprioritizing task queues. Finally, I'll conduct a strategic review to assess progress towards current objectives.\n\nMy immediate focus is on infrastructure and agent health. I'll run quick checks on gateway and session status, look for any critical escalations, and determine if any agents are experiencing extended blockages. These targeted checks will help me maintain system stability and responsiveness.\n\n```\nThe self-direction process involves reviewing recent signals and potential tasks. I'll evaluate current goals and identify any proactive opportunities. If urgent matters arise, I'll route them to the appropriate specialist. Otherwise, I'll confirm system status with a standard heartbeat acknowledgment.\n```","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"I'll perform the heartbeat check following HEARTBEAT.md."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d3b0041b3ef045e1880a0526","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00fb5fc10b47476da90a48f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa46bb6b27c947748d257b16","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a0534249f12a45b086f4264d","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list","recentMinutes":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":17079,"output":705,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772764311517}}
